Let's take a common word and
Americanize it.
You may think you should
pronounce not like note,
but you need to say nät.
ə
This is a neutral vowel sound
that is so special that it has a
name: the schwa.
ə is the most common
sound in English ...
... and it can be represnted by
any of the vowels!
